        <img src="/images/logo-cortex.png" alt="Legal Cortex" style="width: 2.75rem; height: 2.75rem; border-radius: 50%; object-fit: cover; border: 2px solid rgba(220, 38, 38, 0.3);" />
        <span>Legal Cortex</span>
